features: UNLIKE OTHER COAX CONNECTORS THAT give you a SPOTTY SIGNAL and an INCONSISTENT connection, the G-PLUG 75ohm Standard Shield RG6 Cable provides a solid, RELIABLE CONNECTION and effectively extends your signal, due in part to its nickel-plated brass COMPRESSION connectors – known as the best type of F connectors to shield signals from noise. Our F type connector is compatible with all RG6-wired devices: BROADBAND & high-speed Internet, SATELLITE TV, digital TV, and more.

FRUSTRATED WITH THE LOW QUALITY OF other COAXIAL CABLES that break and STOP FUNCTIONING after just a few weeks – or worse, don’t work from the get-go and FALL APART when you first connect them? At G-PLUG, we pride ourselves on engineering some of the highest-quality, most DURABLE compression coax connectors & cables on the market, so they’re sure to become your reliable go-to. Our hardy DOUBLE RUBBER O-ring is even WEATHER-SEALED, so our extension cable is safe for both INDOOR and OUTDOOR use.

YOUR COMPLETE COAXIAL CONNECTION KIT. Our premium-quality coaxial cable connector set includes everything you need for a FAST, STABLE CONNECTION: 75OHM RG6 Standard Shield Cable, BRASS Compression Connectors (nickel-plated), WATERPROOF and weather-sealed Double Rubber O-Ring for both inside and outside use, LEAD-FREE PVC Jacket, and an EASY-ROTATE Nut for connecting to your device. Also includes an EXTRA EXTENSION COUPLER, so you can connect multiple cables and extend your total cord length!

OUR CUSTOMER PROMISE: At G-PLUG, we’re committed to our customers’ ABSOLUTE SATISFACTION. If for any reason you aren’t thrilled with your internet and TV aerial extension cable within 30 DAYS of purchase, simply contact us directly to send back your undamaged coaxial cable compression connector set, and we will return your F connector to coax cable PAYMENT IN FULL. We also offer a 12-MONTH warranty on our compression coaxial connector and cable for a free REPLACEMENT or full reimbursement.
